        "Dear Roy,",
        "I am writing to you to express my sincere apologies regarding the huge noise which is making you inconvenience due  to some drilling work in my garden area as there is some plantation work in progress and it may take a while to get complete and I would request you to please excuse me for another  two days to complete the work.",
